t-bone 's spiritual sons if you 've ever liked the t-bone walker style , or drooled over the pure t-bone licks that both ronnie and duke have graced us with over the years , `` two bones and a pick '' is eight minutes of pure jump-blues-guitar-heaven . i can , and do listen to this for hours on end . if any two white guys have got that jump-blues-guitar-thang down , it 's these two . t-bone is grinning like a cheshire cat